14 to 32 Westchester Square (Lane Ave.), north side, east from its point of junction with Westchester Ave., to its point of junction with East Tremont Ave. The vantage point is Westchester Ave. underneath the elevated structure of the I.R.T. Pelham Bay Park subway
line.
August 25, 1935.
P. L. Sperr.
